♫ <i>The heart gradually responds,</i> ♫

483
00:43:15,380 --> 00:43:17,659
♫ <i>gradually revives,</i> ♫

484
00:43:17,659 --> 00:43:21,079
♫ <i>gradually swims towards you</i> ♫

485
00:43:21,079 --> 00:43:25,330
♫ <i>Before bidding farewell,</i> ♫

486
00:43:25,330 --> 00:43:28,460
♫ <i>we expect an encounter</i> ♫

487
00:43:29,870 --> 00:43:33,939
♫ <i>As your silhouette weaves</i> ♫

488
00:43:33,939 --> 00:43:39,270
♫ <i>and locks in my nostalgic dream</i> ♫

489
00:43:39,270 --> 00:43:41,970
♫ <i>Before the daybreak,</i> ♫

490
00:43:41,970 --> 00:43:44,359
♫ <i>through the obsession of love,</i> ♫

491
00:43:44,359 --> 00:43:48,190
♫ <i>the yearning flowing through thoughts</i> ♫

492
00:43:48,190 --> 00:43:51,760
♫ <i>There's always a moment</i> ♫

493
00:43:51,760 --> 00:43:57,560
♫ <i>where the wilderness burns in my heart</i> ♫

494
00:43:57,560 --> 00:44:01,000
♫ <i>There's always solicitude</i> ♫

495
00:44:01,000 --> 00:44:07,620
♫ <i>which froze everything between you and me</i> ♫

496
00:44:07,620 --> 00:44:09,910
♫ <i>Meet each other in different time</i> ♫

497
00:44:09,910 --> 00:44:12,289
♫ <i>Encourage each other in different worlds</i> ♫

498
00:44:12,289 --> 00:44:16,859
♫ <i>My longings become a cocoon</i> ♫

499
00:44:16,859 --> 00:44:19,619
♫ <i>Layer after layer</i> ♫

500
00:44:19,619 --> 00:44:21,560
♫ <i>It turns into an eternity</i> ♫

